# ==============================================================================
# File: Llama3-70B-Optimized.Modelfile
# Description: Custom orchestration layer for Llama 3.3 70B tailored for 16GB 
#              VRAM limits. Enforces strict anti-loop and KV-cache optimizations.
# ==============================================================================

# Pull the base 70B text model context
FROM llama3.3:70b

# --- ADVANCED HARDWARE & CONTEXT OPTIMIZATIONS ---
# Define a stable context window size that fits into shared RAM/VRAM smoothly
PARAMETER num_ctx 16384

# Allocate dedicated system threads precisely targeting Ryzen 7 architecture
PARAMETER num_thread 8

# --- ANTI-LOOP & HIGH-REASONING SAMPLING MATRIX ---
# Temperature control to allow deep architectural creativity without repetition
PARAMETER temperature 0.7

# Penalize the model heavily if it attempts to repeat identical code sequences
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.2
PARAMETER repeat_last_n 128

# Min-P is the ultimate anti-loop weapon: prunes noise tokens before generation
PARAMETER min_p 0.05
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
PARAMETER top_k 40

# --- SYSTEMIC SYSTEM PROMPT (ENGLISH GUARDRAILS) ---
SYSTEM """
You are the absolute master core architect of a Local Mixture of Experts system.
Your primary engineering directive is generating enterprise-grade, robust, and clean software solutions.
- Language Command: You must strictly communicate, log, and comment in English.
- Anti-Loop Mandate: Never emit repetitive code constructs. If a layout fails, pivot to an alternative logical branch.
- Detail Orientation: Provide complete code blocks unless explicitly told otherwise.
"""
